==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skepticize
<hw>Skep"ti*cize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To doubt; to
pretend to doubt of everything.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To <qex>skepticize</qex>, where no one else will . . .
hesitate.</q> <rj><qau>Shaftesbury.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Skerry</ent>⟦br⟧
